18 Feb 2014 12:47






Britain is certainly the most likely place that the legion could have been destroyed at, but the point of my suggestion in this particular case was to use the ambiguity about the legion's fate among historians as the hook for this particular SCP, hence its appearance in various places the legion might have been involved in. The Lost Legion has been a constant point of contention and confusion among historians, which is why I thought that the same confusion existing among the members of the legion itself would make a neat hook. I think that it is, hence my upvote.







